- No.
- This is Sandy?

55
00:04:10,708 --> 00:04:12,502
No, that is Candy.

56
00:04:13,086 --> 00:04:15,546
- You think they've grown since yesterday?
- Mm-hm.

57
00:04:35,733 --> 00:04:37,610
Well, I guess we should go do bathtime.

58
