Got it. Alex, what are you drinking? Pop?

73
00:06:27,970 --> 00:06:28,970
Alex?

74
00:06:29,430 --> 00:06:31,474
Alex, what do you wanna drink?

75
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:35,269
