205
00:19:47,269 --> 00:19:50,480
<i>♪ You never got the chance to know me ♪</i>

206
00:19:53,192 --> 00:19:54,192
<i>♪ Packed it up... ♪</i>

207
00:19:54,610 --> 00:19:55,861
Come on, Mommy.

208
00:19:58,989 --> 00:20:02,743
<i>♪ You left behind more than memories ♪</i>

209
00:20:03,911 --> 00:20:08,373
<i>♪ Now when I sleep
I'm only dreaming of your face... ♪</i>

210
00:20:10,834 --> 00:20:12,836
